"text_rep": "0.0s: a cat drinking from a glass of beer on a desk next to a pen and a computer mouse on top of it.
1.0s: a cat is drinking from a glass of beer on a desk in front of a computer mouse and a pen on a desk.
2.0s: a cat drinking from a glass of beer on a desk next to a keyboard and a computer mouse on top of it.
3.0s: a cat drinking from a glass of beer on a desk next to a pen and a computer mouse on the desk next to it.
4.0s: a person is sitting on a desk with their hand on a computer keyboard and a pen on the desk next to them.
5.0s: a blurry image of a person sitting in a chair with a computer screen in the back of the chair and a dog in the front of the chair.
6.0s: a laptop sitting on top of a desk with an open book on top of the laptop and a pen on the desk.
"
